Gilded Floral | Cream and Gold All In One Wedding Invitation

Top 5! Gilded Floral | Cream and Gold All In One Wedding Invitation – weddings Cream and Gold All In One Wedding Invitation Have a promotion during this period Gilded Floral quality products and have the highest number of reviews in the same categoryThis gilded floral cream and gold all in one wedding invitation is perfect for an elegant wedding. The modern boho design features a whimsical arrangement of faux gold foil hand drawn flowers, leaves and botanicals on a cream background. Save paper by including the details on the back of the wedding invitation instead of on a separate enclosure card. Include the RSVP info as well if your guest will be replying electronically (optional).

For this design without details on the back, please see this listing: https://www.zazzle.com/256057779040692494

Please Note: This design does not feature real gold foil. It is a high quality graphic made to look like gold foil. Price:$1.88
